Package tech.hiddenproject.progressive.storage

Interface ReflectedCacheableStorageEntity<I>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - Entity id type
    All Superinterfaces:
    ReflectedStorageEntity<I>, StorageEntity<I>
    public interface ReflectedCacheableStorageEntity<I>
extends ReflectedStorageEntity<I>
    Implementation of StorageEntity which collects field values with reflection. Unlike ReflectedStorageEntity EntityMetadata will be cached and field values will be collected only once on ReflectedStorageEntity.init() call. Your entity class must implement saveMetadata(EntityMetadata) to save EntityMetadata internally.
    Author:
    Danila Rassokhin
